name: Liquid Reflections #1
description: Liquid Reflections Series examines the possibilities of using liquid forms and symmetry to create abstract images. Each image is a fight between order and chaos, where order imposed by the symmetry clashes with the fluidity of colours that cannot be contained in their boundaries. It is a fight of contradicting forces that govern our lives. Series consists of 8 artworks, each work is 4000x4000 pixels. This is the multi-edition-low-cost OBJKT of the series where others are 2/2 OBJKTs.
